description: Now kids can take their Puppy Dog Pal on an adventure with the Disney Junior Puppy Dog Pals Groom and Go Pet Carrier! This adorable carrier includes a soft plush Keia puppy and seven accessories to help kids groom and take care of their Puppy Dog Pal! The carrier features a handle for easy carrying and a cute paw-print shaped window so kids can check on their pup. Use the brush to groom Keia's soft coat and the pretend food and water bowl to keep Keia full and happy! When kids are done caring for their pup, it's time for play with the included chew toy! The Puppy Dog Pals Groom and Go Pet Carrier has everything kids need to care for and play with their sweet puppy friend! Collect all three Groom and Go Pet Carriers (each sold separately) including Bingo, Rolly and Keia for the ultimate puppy adventure! Ages 3+
